headline: Alliant Energy Corporation declares quarterly common stock dividend
summary: MADISON, Wis., October 17, 2025--The Alliant Energy Corporation (NASDAQ: LNT) Board of Directors yesterday declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.5075 per share payable on November 17, 2025, to shareowners of record as of the close of business on October 31, 2025.
